  "plainText": "Exclusive to:\nTab Icon.\nThe Renovate Tab is a crafting category exclusive to the Hamlet DLC. It is only accessible while standing inside Slanty Shanty.\nContents\n1 Craftable Items and Structures\n2 Subordinate Tabs\n3 Trivia\n4 Bugs\n5 Gallery\nCraftable Items and Structures[edit | edit source]\nThe following items and structures can be acquired in the Renovate Tab:\nHouse Expansion Permit\nDemolition Permit\nSubordinate Tabs[edit | edit source]\nThe following tabs can be found under the Renovate Tab:\nFloors Tab\nShelves Tab\nPlantholders Tab\nColumns Tab\nWallpaper Tab\nHanging Lamps Tab\nOrnaments Tab\nChairs Tab\nHome Kits Tab\nDoors Tab\nWindows Tab\nRugs Tab\nLamps Tab\nTables Tab\nTrivia[edit | edit source]\nThe Wood Panelling texture resembles the walls of Wilson/Wagstaff's house as seen in the short Forbidden Knowledge.\nBugs[edit | edit source]\nSpawning most items and structures in this tab using the Console will crash the game.\nGallery[edit | edit source]\nRope Wall Panneling texture.\nWood Paneling texture.\nWood Paneling looks similar to Wilson/Wagstaff's house walls.\nFloral Wall Paper texture.\nView or edit this template\nDon't Starve Crafting Tabs\nRegular\nTools\nLight\nSurvival\nFood\nScience\nFight\nStructures\nRefine\nMagic\nDress\n(Nautical )\n(Treasure Hunting )\nCharacter-Specific\nBooks\nTinkering\n(Green Thumb )\nNon-prototypable\nAncient\nVolcanic\n(Renovate\nCity Planning )",
