  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Hamlet}}\n[[File:Icon Renovate.png|thumb|104x104px|Tab Icon.]]\nThe '''Renovate Tab''' is a crafting category exclusive to the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC. It is only accessible while standing inside [[Slanty Shanty]].\n\n== Craftable Items and Structures ==\nThe following items and structures can be acquired in the Renovate Tab:\n\n<div style=\"clear:both; font-weight: bold\"><gallery columns=\"7\" position=\"center\" widths=\"64\" captionalign=\"center\" captionsize=\"medium\" bordersize=\"none\" spacing=\"medium\" hideaddbutton=\"true\" navigation=\"true\">\nHouse Expansion Permit.png|[[House Expansion Permit]]|link=House Expansion Permit\nDemolition Permit.png|[[Demolition Permit]]|link=Demolition Permit\n</gallery></div>\n\n== Subordinate Tabs ==\nThe following tabs can be found under the Renovate Tab:\n\n<div style=\"clear:both; font-weight: bold\"><gallery columns=\"7\" position=\"center\" widths=\"64\" captionalign=\"center\" captionsize=\"medium\" bordersize=\"none\" spacing=\"medium\" hideaddbutton=\"true\" navigation=\"true\">\nFlooring.png|[[Floors Tab]]|link=Floors Tab\nShelves.png|[[Shelves Tab]]|link=Shelves Tab\nPlantholders.png|[[Plantholders Tab]]|link=Plantholders Tab\nColumns.png|[[Columns Tab]]|link=Columns Tab\nWall Papers.png|[[Wallpaper Tab]]|link=Wallpaper Tab\nCeiling Lights.png|[[Hanging Lamps Tab]]|link=Hanging Lamps Tab\nWall Decorations.png|[[Ornaments Tab]]|link=Ornaments Tab\nChairs.png|[[Chairs Tab]]|link=Chairs Tab\nHouse Upgrades.png|[[Home Kits Tab]]|link=Home Kits Tab\nDoors.png|[[Doors Tab]]|link=Doors Tab\nWindows.png|[[Windows Tab]]|link=Windows Tab\nRugs.png|[[Rugs Tab]]|link=Rugs Tab\nLamps.png|[[Lamps Tab]]|link=Lamps Tab\nTables.png|[[Tables Tab]]|link=Tables Tab\n</gallery></div>\n\n== [[File:Placeholder.png|32px]] Trivia ==\n* The Wood Panelling texture resembles the walls of Wilson/Wagstaff's house as seen in the short ''[[Animated Shorts and Trailers|Forbidden Knowledge]]''.\n\n== [[File:Mosquito.png|32px]] Bugs ==\n* Spawning most items and structures in this tab using the [[Console]] will crash the game.\n\n== [[File:Blueprint.png|32px]] Gallery ==\n<gallery captionalign=\"center\" spacing=\"small\" widths=\"192\" hideaddbutton=\"true\">\nRope wall panneling texture.png|Rope Wall Panneling texture.\nWood panelling texture.png|Wood Paneling texture.\nForbidden Knowledge 9.png|Wood Paneling looks similar to Wilson/Wagstaff's house walls.\nFloral wall paper texture.png|Floral Wall Paper texture.\n</gallery>\n{{Tabs}}\n[[Category:Hamlet]]\n[[Category:Crafting Tabs]]\n[[zh:翻新栏]]\n[[vi:Thẻ Cải Tạo Nhà]]\n[[ko:개조 탭]]"
